remoteTransactionPrepared

public void remoteTransactionPrepared(GlobalTransaction gtx)
Marks the transaction as prepared. If at a further point the originator fails, the transaction is removed form the "normal" transactions collection and moved into the cache that holds in-doubt transactions. See cleanupStaleTransactions(org.infinispan.topology.CacheTopology)
